1. Go to the Ops Manager Installation Dashboard.

1. Click **Review Pending Changes**.

1. Select the <%= vars.app_runtime_abbr %> and <%= vars.windows_runtime_abbr %> tiles and review the changes. For more information, see [Reviewing Pending Product Changes](https://docs.pivotal.io/ops-manager/2-10/install/review-pending-changes.html).

